{"tid":704643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「媽媽不在，妳要滿足爸爸」新北鬼父洗腦9年　調教女兒當性奴","createTime":"2018-06-16T14:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T05:15:11.000Z","uid":176366,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4b27d801f6980f0150a184bd68f587678a4cf41a","tid":704643,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3155/d3155954.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3155%2Fd3155954.jpg&h=4a948d9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲鬼父性侵猥褻女兒多年，直到大女兒升上國二，全案才曝光。（示意圖／取自pakutaso）<br />\n<br />\n社會中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n新北市一名單親鬼父獨自扶養2名女兒，卻從小到大灌輸「媽媽已離開，爸爸有需要，妳應該讓爸爸滿足」的偏差觀念，要年幼的2個女兒供他洩慾；直到大女兒上國中，把事情告訴男友，鬼父淫行才徹底曝光。<br />\n<br />\n根據檢警調查，現年40歲的鬼父與妻子離婚後，獨自照料2個女兒，卻從2008年8月開始，向年僅5歲的大女兒伸出狼爪，灌輸「妳應該代替媽媽、滿足爸爸」等偏差觀念，誘導大女兒同意供他性交洩慾。<br />\n<br />\n事後，鬼父食髓知味，2010年10月開始對年僅4歲的小女兒猥褻、性交。而姊妹花也彼此知道父親淫行，但因為父親是家中支柱，加上多年來觀念洗腦，所以一直默默隱忍。<br />\n<br />\n直到大女兒去年升上國中二年級，向男友吐露父親所為，男友才氣得轉告學校輔導老師，揭發鬼父性侵惡行。<br />\n<br />\n鬼父到案後，向警方坦承犯行，還在社工、親人面前下跪認錯，豈料接受檢方偵訊時卻突然翻供，辯稱是因為母親住院，他到警所後一時不知所措，又擔心女兒沒人照顧，才向警方說「有」，這樣一來社會局就會介入照顧。<br />\n<br />\n鬼父說，他之前沒收2個女兒的手機，一時衝動動手教導，才讓2個女兒懷恨在心、惡意誣陷。但由於兩姊妹指證歷歷，又有社工說詞為證，檢方最後認定大女兒遭性侵193次、猥褻191次，二女兒則被性侵271次，猥褻814次，21日依加重強制性交、猥褻及對未滿14歲女子性交及猥褻罪嫌將鬼父起訴。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03557ac1f4814c1fc3cf7aad0ecb31b41f6ea3a4","tid":704643,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:49:53.000Z","msg":"來源:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180322/1135219.htm#ixzz5IbF8gBlW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180322%2F1135219.htm%23ixzz5IbF8gBlW&d=8%2FecTCk65bD14FcamYlLIpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=3706f0ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180322/1135219.htm#ixzz5IbF8gBlW</a><div style=\"text-align: left;\"></div>"},{"pid":"e76665b9251eb4d5832b64be5757442ebf327263","tid":704643,"uid":137233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:50:29.000Z","msg":"寶島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491e8e68725aea7233f06e77a6c2b2533b44588f","tid":704643,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff144fb28c2541bc7bc2dfbdb2afc84f63dd424","tid":704643,"uid":128731,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:52:03.000Z","msg":"點樣可以驗到次數咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad7bec2f9bae5270c0f25683891d1215740db2a","tid":704643,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:53:17.000Z","msg":"台灣最美的風景<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d97c23512e381142bd446ee7cbafd8af5fbff65f","tid":704643,"uid":45477,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:56:32.000Z","msg":"呢個島真係冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71992f8f3c7c476d51a499b47e0caf363e7f7f2","tid":704643,"uid":28668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:59:02.000Z","msg":"所以話台灣"},{"pid":"a82ecb24e3365ab55b3f8f05c01d7e54a7a7c2e9","tid":704643,"uid":68944,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T03:38:47.000Z","msg":"檢方最後認定大女兒遭性侵193次、猥褻191次，二女兒則被性侵271次，猥褻814次<br />\n<br />\n二女兒靚啲？"},{"pid":"a3f9d07d7a3ccd8e5eae3183bb275fa62c1cd599","tid":704643,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03557ac1f4814c1fc3cf7aad0ecb31b41f6ea3a4","tid":704643,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:49:53.000Z","msg":"來源:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180322/1135219.htm#ixzz5IbF8gBlW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180322%2F1135219.htm%23ixzz5IbF8gBlW&d=8%2FecTCk65bD14FcamYlLIpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=3706f0ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180322/1135219.htm#ixzz5IbF8gBlW</a><div style=\"text-align: left;\"></div>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T03:42:11.000Z","msg":"做乜貼舊聞？"},{"pid":"e17a943ccc99219c277d2472c4f87d548b07e708","tid":704643,"uid":143131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T03:43:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所</span></span>"},{"pid":"5ae0dc4c8cf4093d757ae47d229e1265ee7b7489","tid":704643,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T03:44:52.000Z","msg":"台灣就黎要同印度一樣咁搞,強姦犯要化學閹割 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac06249af2cffcab8cd71cb3abc0b153862c0ab","tid":704643,"uid":191017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T03:46:21.000Z","msg":"台灣+1分<br />\n同印度爭第1<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5ea0f8b7185d97593a155aeb5fb27fec9f819b","tid":704643,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a82ecb24e3365ab55b3f8f05c01d7e54a7a7c2e9","tid":704643,"uid":68944,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T03:38:47.000Z","msg":"檢方最後認定大女兒遭性侵193次、猥褻191次，二女兒則被性侵271次，猥褻814次<br />\n<br />\n二女兒靚啲？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T03:46:22.000Z","msg":"一定緊Ｄ"},{"pid":"1bdbac741e4d1c3b1d2f11aae31f402616732dda","tid":704643,"uid":173342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T03:48:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74fa2045df7e3b1a3eaf47e4edc54cd4596fc921","tid":704643,"uid":86097,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T03:49:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"713c387ff8850f17edc05d53c0e658410c63caa2","tid":704643,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb5ea0f8b7185d97593a155aeb5fb27fec9f819b","tid":704643,"uid":72